document_data.name: Six Coffers Market Priakos
document_data.mainbody: The '''Six Coffers Market Priakos''' was a merchant company in [[Faer√ªn]].
document_data.History: Originally founded by six merchants, only four of the remaining founders remained alive in [[1367 DR]]. [[Thelve Baruinheld]] served as the leader of the organization, operating out of [[Berdusk]].
document_data.Base of Operations: This merchant company had bases of operation in Berdusk, [[Waterdeep]], [[Silverymoon]], [[Priapurl]], and [[Selgaunt]].
